<br>
at level 60 with identical equipment ( +100str +108sta)<br>
<br>
1. dark elf warrior would be at 195str 183sta (about 3500hps)<br>
<br>
2. ogre warrior would be at 240str 255sta (about 3900hps)<br>
<br>
What suprised me was that the desparity at level 50 (400hps) to level 60 was the same HP difference between the weakest stated warrior class and the strongest. The difference in HP's is only 11 percent at level 60 but at level 50 its almost 18percent....just something to think about.<br>
<br>
Another point which was made in these posts is that now that the ogre has maxed stamina he can now move to the other stat catagory's and improve them as he sees fit, while the dark elf will still try to improve on stamina to get his hps up.<br>
<br>
NOTE: this comparison was made with high end equipment but certainly obtainable by anyone level 60 in a good guild....<br>
<br>
hope this clears things up<br>
